            "critical_failure": "As failure, but if the target is already stupefied by Label Memories, they become paralyzed for 1 minute instead of confused.",
            "critical_success": "The target creature is unaffected and temporarily immune to Label Memories for 1 minute.",
            "failure": "The target becomes stupefied 2 for 1 minute as its mind is reorganized to fit the rhu-chalik's needs. If it's already stupefied by this effect, the target instead becomes confused for 1 minute or until it recovers due to taking damage.",
